document.discussion_title: League One | Agard becomes MK Dons record signing
document.topic_text: 11.08.2016 - 16:49 | Source: Milton Keynes Dons Agard becomes MK Dons record signing League One Milton Keynes Dons have completed the transfer of 26-year-old Kieran Agard , who joins for a club-record transfer fee which remains undisclosed. The Bristol City striker, who made six games for Everton , has signed a three-year contract with the League One club.
